org.cpsolver.ifs.example.jobshop

Class Job

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.model.Constraint<Operation,Location>
      • org.cpsolver.ifs.example.jobshop.Job
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Constraint<Operation,Location>>

    public class Job
extends Constraint<Operation,Location>
    Job constraint.

    Each job contians a given set of operations (variables). A job constraint is satisfied, if all operations of the job do not overlap in time and are processed in the given order.
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)
